# S03-T02: Attitude Gauges

## Objective
Port AttitudeGauges (201 lines, CSS) to React with Tailwind classes (no Canvas).

## Acceptance Criteria
- `src/features/hud/gauges/AttitudeGauges.tsx` renders three indicators: ROLL, PITCH, YAW.
- Roll/Pitch as bar indicators; YAW as compass strip.
- Smooth value updates via Framer Motion `animate()` (200ms ease-out).
- Labels uppercase, JetBrains Mono per UI_REGULATION.

## Steps
1. Build `<BarIndicator>` primitive with min/max/value/label props.
2. Build `<CompassStrip>` primitive (translateX based on yaw degrees).
3. Compose into `<AttitudeGauges>`.
4. Bind to `useTelemetryStore.attitude`.

## Invariants
- All transforms GPU-accelerated (translate3d/transform).
- No spring/bounce — strict ease-out (UI_REGULATION).
- Component memoized at root; child primitives leaf-level memoized.
